    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Output comparison NRMSE of 9.4% satisfies the 15% threshold. Grid convergence study demonstrates discretization error below 5% for primary QoI. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed at all five evaluated operating points, supporting the regulatory submission decision.",
